#- Abandoned City History of Central City
Coordinates: (-6200, -7000) Nether Coordinates: (-776, 36, -898)
Central City is an abandoned, griefed city. It had a fair number of residents during summer 2012. It was griefed
#- continually by many including 7583 and Baliskos as its wealth was enough to attract griefers but not enough to deter them. Eventually, most of its residents quit the server or moved elsewhere and it gradually became a ghost town.
#- This is originally the work of writers on the Civcraft Wiki, last modified by alex9002, September 5, 2012, and transcribed for Minecraft book and quill by Librarian Orikebise, of the Agora State University
